{"word":"H1523 - גִּיל - gîyl - gheel - Be glad","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גִּיל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>gîyl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>gheel"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be glad"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பூரி, களிகூர், மகிழ், ஆனந்தமாய் இரு, களிகூர்ந்திரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to rejoice, to exult, to be glad (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"a) to rejoice"},{"paragraph":"b) to tremble (from fear)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>spin</i> around (under the influence of any violent emotion), that is, usually <i>rejoice</i>, or (as <i>cringing</i>) <i>fear: - </i>be glad, joy, be joyful, rejoice."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1523 - גִּיל - gîyl - gheel/1523\">H1523</a>, <a href=\"#/H1524 - גִּיל - gîyl - gheel/1524\">H1524</a>, <a href=\"#/H1525 - גִּילָה - gîylâh - ghee-law'/1525\">H1525</a>, <a href=\"#/H1526 - גִּילֹנִי - Gîylônîy - ghee-lo-nee'/1526\">H1526</a>, <a href=\"#/H1542 - גִּלֹה - Gilôh - ghee-lo'/1542\">H1542</a>"}]}